  "texts": [
    "Moreover, blockchain-based systems are designed to be immutable, meaning that once a transaction is added to the blockchain, it cannot be changed.",
    "This feature is important for maintaining the integrity and security of the system, but it can also make it difficult to correct errors or mistakes made by an AI agent.",
    "This lack of flexibility and adaptability in blockchain-based systems could limit their effectiveness in certain use cases involving AI.",
    "Finally, the integration of blockchain and AI raises concerns about data privacy and security.",
    "AI agents rely on large amounts of data to train and make decisions, and blockchain-based systems are designed to be transparent and secure."
  ],
